Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 3: Even a Hero Needs to Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no money!\NEpisode 3: Even a Hero Needs to Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?\NWe can't even stay at an inn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to use our last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean making money with\Nyour body, like always?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I always imagine doing it,\Nand I get all flushed and excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I don't actually do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's our last resort, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are heroes.  The law protects us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. We are heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As per the Special Hero Dispensation Act,\Nwe will be taking needed items!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,those given the task of saving the world by\Nthe national government are called heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Special Hero Dispensation Act
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,gives them the right to take needed items\Nfrom treasure chests and dressers in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's search this place\Nfrom top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Herb.  Antidote.  10 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all this gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make very good use of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A wizard's staff!\NI've always wanted one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for us to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a higher purpose: to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And small sacrifices must be made\Nto achieve that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're hitting that place next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.  I'm a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A fighter's steel broadsword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh... excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!  A philosopher's stone?  Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I save up more money,\NI'm gonna buy Daddy a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!  This is all to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Special Hero Dispensation Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not in danger of going broke anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get to stay in such a\Nwonderful hotel... it's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Special Hero Dispensation Act\Nis the best, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The law is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As heroes, let's keep doing our best\Nfor our world and its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They were mad, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're breaking the law... how rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At least... leave us our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'M SORRY!